### ====================================
### DRIVER NOTIFICATION API TESTING
### ====================================
### IMPORTANT: Replace {{DELIVERY_ID}} with actual delivery UUID
### Get it from: GET /api/delivery/active or after creating a delivery
### ====================================

### 1. Driver Send Alert - Traffic Delay
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "traffic_delay",
  "message": "Heavy traffic on highway, expected 2 hours delay to destination",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 2. Driver Send Alert - Puncture
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "puncture",
  "message": "Front left tire punctured. Need assistance at nearest workshop.",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 3. Driver Send Alert - Breakdown
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "breakdown",
  "message": "Engine overheating. Truck stopped on roadside. Need mechanic assistance.",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 4. Driver Send Alert - Fuel Issue
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "fuel_issue",
  "message": "Running low on fuel. Nearest gas station is 50km away.",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 5. Driver Send Alert - Accident
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "accident",
