### 6. Driver Send Alert - Weather Delay
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "weather_delay",
  "message": "Heavy flooding on route. Cannot proceed safely. Waiting for water to recede.",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 7. Driver Send Alert - Custom Message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "driver_message",
  "message": "Taking a short rest break. Will continue in 30 minutes.",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### ====================================
### VIEW ALERTS (Admin/Owner/Driver)
### ====================================

### 8. Get Active Delivery Details (includes all alerts)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/detail
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

### 9. Get Delivery Detail by ID (Admin/Owner)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/detail/{{DELIVERY_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}

### 10. Get All Active Deliveries (Admin/Owner)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/active
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}

### 11. Get Driver's Delivery History (includes past alerts)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/history
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

### ====================================
### CREATE DELIVERY (Prerequisite for Alerts)
### ====================================

### 12. Create a New Delivery (Operator/Admin only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}

{
  "truckId": "truck-id-here",
  "routeId": "route-id-here",
  "workerId": "driver-id-here",
  "latitude": -6.2088,
  "longitude": 106.8456
}

### 13. Get Available Trucks (before creating delivery)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trucks/available
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}

### ====================================
### ERROR CASES TESTING
### ====================================

### 14. Error: Non-driver trying to send alert
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_ADMIN}}

{
  "type": "puncture",
  "message": "Test from admin",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 15. Error: Missing required type field
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "message": "Missing type field",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 16. Error: Missing required message field
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "puncture",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 17. Error: Invalid alert type
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "INVALID_TYPE",
  "message": "This should fail",
  "deliveryId": "{{DELIVERY_ID}}"
}

### 18. Error: No active delivery found (no deliveryId provided)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/alert/send
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

{
  "type": "puncture",
  "message": "No active delivery"
}

### ====================================
### AUTO-DETECTION TESTING (System Alerts)
### ====================================

### Note: Auto-detection runs every 5 minutes
### To test GPS_LOST alert:
###   1. Start a delivery
###   2. Stop sending position updates
###   3. Wait 10+ minutes
###   4. Check delivery detail for gps_lost alert

### To test ILLEGAL_STOP alert:
###   1. Start a delivery
###   2. Keep GPS at same location
###   3. Wait 45+ minutes
###   4. Check delivery detail for illegal_stop alert

### 19. Check for Auto-Generated Alerts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/delivery/detail
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_DRIVER}}

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "alerts": [
###     {
###       "id": "alert-id",
###       "type": "gps_lost",
###       "message": "No GPS update...",
###       "createdAt": 1234567890,
###       "senderId": null,
###       "senderUsername": null
###     }
###   ]
### }
